Read MBR4.0 data from Martin Systems Webportal (As "tsv")

Source: R/read_mbr4.R
read_mbr4_latest.Rd

Read MBR4.0 data from Martin Systems Webportal (As "tsv")

read_mbr4_latest(
  url = Sys.getenv("MBR4.0_URL"),
  target_dir = tempdir(),
  dbg = FALSE,
  ...
)

Arguments

url

url to download site (default: Sys.getenv("MBR4.0_URL"), please use run edit_r_environ and define a key value pair "MBR4.0_URL" = "download-url-martin-systems") so that this function works automatically
target_dir

directory to download data (default: tempdir())
dbg

print debug messages (default: FALSE)
...

additional arguments passed to read_tsv

Value

tibble with imported MBR4.0 tsv data (~ last four weeks)

Examples

mbr4_data_latest <- read_mbr4_latest()

#> New names:
